I, the applicant for prior approval for the overseas study, acknowledge that all statements contained in this application are true and have full legal liability and all the consequences of the failure to provide the correct information.
I also undertake that if I receive my application, I am committed to the study criteria mentioned in the approval decision and the necessary procedures:
- No change of state - University - specialization - the school stage only with the approval of the administration of the equivalence of university degrees
- To be the study and tests at the university headquarters
- The duration of the study shall be less than three and a half years for the bachelor's degree
- Commitment to not equivalent to any school hours do not comply with the regulations in force in the Ministry of Education and Higher Education.
To enroll in the study as of the date specified in the university admission letter, and in case of failure to join the deadline, apply again for prior approval in accordance with the new conditions and standards.
